        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1393152932" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9256768728490701935">A good book based during the Civil War. Takes place in St. Louis and includes a lot of St. Louis history, including the role of German settlers and a look at the way the city was divided between confederates and rebels.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


